data.name: oracleSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT G.COURSE, GET_GROUPNAME(G.NAME_GROUP, G.COURSE, G.SUBGROUP) AS GROUPNAME, GET_FULLNAME(S.LAST_NAME, S.FIRST_NAME, S.THIRD_NAME) AS FULLNAME, M.VALUE_MARK, M.DATE_MARK, GET_DISCNAME(D.ID_DISCNAME) AS DISCNAME FROM MARKS M, STUDENTS S, "GROUPS" G, DISCIPLINES D WHERE M.ID_STUDENT = S.ID_STUDENT AND S.ID_GROUP = G.ID_GROUP AND M.ID_DISCIPLINE = D.ID_DISCIPLINE AND (S.ID_STATUS = 1) ORDER BY GROUPNAME, FULLNAME

data.name: oracleSelectCommand8.CommandText
data.value: SELECT ID_DISCIPLINE, get_discname_with_groupname(ID_DISCNAME, ID_GROUP) AS DISCNAME, ID_GROUP FROM DISCIPLINES WHERE (ID_DISCIPLINE IN (SELECT DISCIPLINES_ID_DISCIPLINE FROM TEACHERS2DISCIPLINES WHERE (TEACHERS_ID_TEACHER = :tid))) ORDER BY DISCNAME

data.name: oracleUpdateCommand3.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE "DISCIPLINES" SET "ID_DISCIPLINE" = :ID_DISCIPLINE, "ID_GROUP" = :ID_GROUP WHERE (("ID_DISCIPLINE" = :Original_ID_DISCIPLINE) AND ((:IsNull_ID_GROUP = 1 AND "ID_GROUP" IS NULL) OR ("ID_GROUP" = :Original_ID_GROUP)))

data.name: oracleSelectCommand9.CommandText
data.value: SELECT m.ID_MARK, m.VALUE_MARK, get_fullname(s.LAST_NAME, s.FIRST_NAME, s.THIRD_NAME) AS STUDNAME, get_fullname(t.LAST_NAME, t.FIRST_NAME, t.THIRD_NAME) AS TEACHNAME, get_discname_with_groupname(d.ID_DISCNAME, d.ID_GROUP) AS DISCNAME FROM MARKS m, STUDENTS s, TEACHERS t, DISCIPLINES d WHERE s.ID_STUDENT = m.ID_STUDENT AND t.ID_TEACHER = m.ID_TEACHER AND d.ID_DISCIPLINE = m.ID_DISCIPLINE AND (m.ID_DISCIPLINE = :did) AND (m.ID_TEACHER = :tid) ORDER BY STUDNAME

data.name: oracleSelectCommand12.CommandText
data.value: SELECT m.VALUE_MARK, m.DATE_MARK, get_fullname(t.LAST_NAME, t.FIRST_NAME, t.THIRD_NAME) AS FULLNAME, get_discname(d.ID_DISCNAME) AS DISCNAME FROM MARKS m, TEACHERS t, DISCIPLINES d WHERE t.ID_TEACHER = m.ID_TEACHER AND d.ID_DISCIPLINE = m.ID_DISCIPLINE AND (m.ID_STUDENT = :sid) AND (m.ID_DISCIPLINE IN (SELECT ID_DISCIPLINE FROM DISCIPLINES d2 WHERE (ID_GROUP = :gid))) ORDER BY m.DATE_MARK

data.name: oracleSelectCommand14.CommandText
data.value: SELECT s.ID_STUDENT, get_fullname(s.LAST_NAME, s.FIRST_NAME, s.THIRD_NAME) AS FULLNAME, g.COURSE FROM STUDENTS s, "GROUPS" g WHERE g.ID_GROUP = s.ID_GROUP AND (s.ID_GROUP = :idg) AND (to_date(s.EXPIRY_STATUS, 'DD-MM-RR') = to_date(sysdate, 'DD-MM-RR'))

data.name: oracleUpdateCommand8.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE "TEACHERS" SET "ID_TEACHER" = :ID_TEACHER, "LAST_NAME" = :LAST_NAME, "FIRST_NAME" = :FIRST_NAME, "THIRD_NAME" = :THIRD_NAME, "PASSWOD" = :PASSWOD WHERE (("ID_TEACHER" = :Original_ID_TEACHER) AND ((:IsNull_LAST_NAME = 1 AND "LAST_NAME" IS NULL) OR ("LAST_NAME" = :Original_LAST_NAME)) AND ((:IsNull_FIRST_NAME = 1 AND "FIRST_NAME" IS NULL) OR ("FIRST_NAME" = :Original_FIRST_NAME)) AND ((:IsNull_THIRD_NAME = 1 AND "THIRD_NAME" IS NULL) OR ("THIRD_NAME" = :Original_THIRD_NAME)) AND ((:IsNull_PASSWOD = 1 AND "PASSWOD" IS NULL) OR ("PASSWOD" = :Original_PASSWOD)))

data.name: oracleDeleteCommand8.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM "TEACHERS" WHERE (("ID_TEACHER" = :Original_ID_TEACHER) AND ((:IsNull_LAST_NAME = 1 AND "LAST_NAME" IS NULL) OR ("LAST_NAME" = :Original_LAST_NAME)) AND ((:IsNull_FIRST_NAME = 1 AND "FIRST_NAME" IS NULL) OR ("FIRST_NAME" = :Original_FIRST_NAME)) AND ((:IsNull_THIRD_NAME = 1 AND "THIRD_NAME" IS NULL) OR ("THIRD_NAME" = :Original_THIRD_NAME)) AND ((:IsNull_PASSWOD = 1 AND "PASSWOD" IS NULL) OR ("PASSWOD" = :Original_PASSWOD)))

data.name: oracleSelectCommand16.CommandText
data.value: SELECT m.value_mark, get_fullname(s.last_name, s.first_name, s.third_name) AS FULLNAME, get_discname_with_groupname(d2.id_discname, d2.id_group) AS DISCNAME FROM marks m JOIN disciplines d2 ON d2.id_discipline = m.id_discipline JOIN students s ON s.id_student = m.id_student WHERE (m.id_discipline in ( SELECT d.id_discipline FROM disciplines d WHERE (d.id_group IN ( SELECT id_group FROM groups )) )) AND (m.value_mark < 3) AND (s.id_status = 1)
